










****blocking and non blocking***

blocking::
if thread doing one task like file read then it will not perform after task till file read compelted

non blocking:
task 1 : file read(after excution return callback )
task 2 : Http request (after excution return callback )

till file read complete it will complete 2nd task http request

*************************Callback**********************


last parameter of function is
call in last of function is excution
1 st parameter is error or null

// example::


// function dosomething(callback){

//     const user =  getalluser((err, data) => {
// if(err) return callback(err)
// callback(null,data)


//     })
// }
 